ALGORITHM

1.	Start
2.	Initialize DPTR to 4600H
3.	Read the number from memory location 4600H and store it in R1 register
4.	Increment DPTR and read the value from next memory location and store it to accumulator
5.	Subtract the value of R1 register and accumulator and store the result to the accumulator
6.	If carry flag is set, increment R2 register 
7.	Increment DPTR and store the value of Accumulator to memory location 4602H
8.	Increment DPTR and store the value of R2 register to memory location 4603H
9.	Stop

